      <title>罗杰斯预计，Shaw 交易后 2024 年现金流量将增加 20%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/rogers-beats-sees-20-cash-flow-boost-in-2024-after-shaw-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗杰斯通信公司 (Rogers Communications Inc.) 第四季度业绩超出分析师预期，并发布了 2024 年乐观前景，预测服务收入将至少增长 8%，自由现金流将大幅增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/rogers-beats-sees-20-cash-flow-boost-in-2024-after-shaw-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 12:28:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行预计 2024 年南非家庭支出依然疲弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/hsbc-sees-south-africa-household-spending-remaining-weak-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰全球研究 (HSBC Global Research) 的一项研究显示，除全球金融危机和 Covid-19 封锁之外，南非的家庭消费去年可能以三十年来最弱的速度增长，预计到 2024 年将小幅回升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/hsbc-sees-south-africa-household-spending-remaining-weak-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 12:27:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行维持关键利率 5.25% 不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-01/bank-of-england-holds-key-rate-unchanged-at-5-25</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行以三路投票表决将基准利率维持在5.25%，其中两名成员投票支持加息，一名成员投票支持降息。莉兹·伯登 (Lizzy Burden) 接受彭博电视台报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-01/bank-of-england-holds-key-rate-unchanged-at-5-25</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 12:24:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果通胀缓和，英国央行上调 2024 年降息的预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/bank-of-england-signals-rate-cuts-possible-once-inflation-eases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行打开了降息的大门，大幅下调了今年的通胀前景，并放弃了借贷成本可能不得不再次上升的指引。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/bank-of-england-signals-rate-cuts-possible-once-inflation-eases</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 12:00:04 GMT</pubDate>
